<em>Eric S. Bland, a lawyer for the Hammond family, has demanded that the news media treat the killing of Mr. Hammond as they have recent shootings of unarmed black men, and some supporters on social media agree. </em></p>
<div class="w75 left"><figure class="media photo promo" itemprop="" itemscope="" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/08/01/us/01missingteens/01missingteens-thumbStandard.jpg" itemtype="//schema.org/ImageObject" role="group"><span class="visually-hidden">Photo</span><div class="image"><img itemprop="url" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/08/01/us/01missingteens/01missingteens-thumbStandard.jpg" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/08/01/us/01missingteens/01missingteens-thumbStandard.jpg" id="100000003830565" width="75" height="75" alt="Lanterns were released Tuesday during a vigil for the missing teenagers, Austin Stephanos and Perry Cohen, in Stuart, Fla."   /><meta itemprop="height" content="75"><meta itemprop="width" content="75"></div></figure></div><p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">
